arts.ttl: Rangers v Genk: Golden Boy’s return from injury ‘good news’ for manager, duo to miss EL clash
arts.sum: KRC Genk will travel to Ibrox to face Rangers in the first group stage match of the Europa League on Thursday. Rangers and the Belgian club have endured difficult starts to the season and both Russell Martin and Thorsten Fink have uncertain futures. arts.ttl: Rangers vs Genk predictions: Genk to deny Gers a much-needed win
